<p class="">The hon. Member for Louth is waiting to take over.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-2e38c273-e477-4901-a7de-482e8a66373a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1954-01-26/debates/e35ae4ed-fbe9-4445-8722-80fdb8950798/CurrencyAndBankNotesBill#contribution-2e38c273-e477-4901-a7de-482e8a66373a">
